{"tid":1296164,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[國會出手]  美國會擬禁軍方買中國製無人機","createTime":"2019-07-08T09:32:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T00:43:56.000Z","uid":141151,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d3cf8ef3144deed4ec3b9e6a8a50f2dfd98a7906","tid":1296164,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T09:32:30.000Z","msg":"美國會擬禁軍方買中國製無人機<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/international/article/2185920\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Finternational%2Farticle%2F2185920&d=ng3vG9SJ7BvQZwuOeCzNpUBo7c%2BYFxEppcXi0rJe94o%3D&h=fff017d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/international/article/2185920</a><br />\n<br />\n美國參議院上周通過《國防授權法案》(National Defense Authorization Act)，將禁止中國無人機用於軍事用途，原因是美國官員愈來愈擔心該國對中國無人機的依賴，可能會危及美國重要的基礎設施，亦擔心無人機會將資訊傳給中國政府或其他地方的黑客，用於實施網絡攻擊或其他違法行為。<br />\n<br />\n該法案的眾議院版本將禁用外國無人機，預期有關版本將在本月稍後進行表決。<br />\n<br />\n威斯康星州共和黨眾議員Michael Gallagher等支持國防部的禁令，表示禁令還將阻止州級和地方機構包括警隊，以及那些使用無人機對設施和運作進行監控的建築、交通運輸和能源公司採購中國無人機。"},{"pid":"bb1fe62b25560c5bf871782c7f0472b225435f52","tid":1296164,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T11:27:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98c991210ac8dd97f5f91ff4ad1cb33ef5476a3e","tid":1296164,"uid":92448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T11:38:17.000Z","msg":"中國製無人機=CCTV=監控軍方"},{"pid":"3a5ce697c5497105a4cfd8b59e7c468aec1d557c","tid":1296164,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T11:54:08.000Z","msg":"其實海康威視更恐怖"},{"pid":"e8c6998064e4cf9614297879349243af6010fa6f","tid":1296164,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T11:57:05.000Z","msg":"之後網絡攻擊原來有無人機"},{"pid":"5b680793469068d47c5e37d7d2184181c58b3fba","tid":1296164,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply